text: Strahinja Stefanović (born 7 March 1998) is a Serbian sprint canoeist.Profile He won a medal at the 2019 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships.2019 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships results ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships medalists in kayak Category:Serbian male canoeists Category:Sportspeople from Novi Sad
